descriptionNullable:
This dataset contains **Dutch energy generation per production type.** The data is updated daily and is always a day behind the current date.

Energy values are in MW.

**Source**: [ENTSOE-E Transparency Platform](https://transparency.entsoe.eu/)

ENTSOE-E is the European association for the cooperation of transmission system operators (TSOs) for electricity.
